%h1 Volunteer Opportunities

%p When registering, a user can be asked to volunteer for any volunteer role.

= radio_button_tag :volunteer_type, "one", VolunteerOpportunity.all.none?, class: "js--displayIfChecked", data: { displayBlock: "js--checkedSourceOne" }
= label_tag :volunteer_type_one, "Ask \"I want to Volunteer\""
%br
= radio_button_tag :volunteer_type, "many", VolunteerOpportunity.all.any?, class: "js--displayIfChecked", data: { displayBlock: "js--checkedSourceMany" }
= label_tag :volunteer_type_many, "Ask \"I want to Volunteer for <role>\""

.generic_results.js--checkedSourceOne
  Every Registrant will be asked "Do you want to Volunteer?""

.specific_results.js--checkedSourceMany
  = render "specific_question_results"
